        <li><strong>Local Schema Markup:</strong> Adding structured data to your website to help search engines understand your location, hours, and services.</li>
        <li><strong>Google Business Profile Optimization:</strong> Regularly updating your GBP with posts, photos, and accurate information.</li>
    </ul>

